{"id":"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale","title":"基於語言環境格式化資料","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"format-data-based-on-locale\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"23u4rd5ufxutyammmlq8zso15\">基於語言環境格式化資料<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#format-data-based-on-locale\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bzyk8u70i5b6vje6drj2ybtxf\">Angular 提供了以下內建的資料轉換<a href=\"guide/glossary#pipe\" title=\"pipe - Glossary | Angular\">通道</a>。資料轉換通道會使用 <a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" title=\"LOCALE_ID | Core - API | Angular\"><code>LOCALE_ID</code></a> 令牌來根據每個語言環境的規則來格式化資料。</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"79p54qfxov65br6dg8fhiv1cf\">資料轉換通道</th>\n<th align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3prlgfrx5eo2xqncnnob4crxu\">詳情</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2qv5jrjz1cbf96roxpg4m8a7b\"><a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" title=\"DatePipe | Common - API | Angular\"><code>DatePipe</code></a></td>\n<td align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1ilx630czcfyt99eekkm6hxga\">格式化日期值。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ekzg44jmibalpk8fvy5qxbm2q\"><a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" title=\"CurrencyPipe | Common - API | Angular\"><code>CurrencyPipe</code></a></td>\n<td align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"egst3fe8wu88rigpkkang7fmp\">將數字轉換為貨幣字串。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dw2o7g2h0xvyj4nrwk2mkdtxl\"><a href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe\" title=\"DecimalPipe | Common - API | Angular\"><code>DecimalPipe</code></a></td>\n<td align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4ncq30xe8x1y85008f8rz4j9p\">將數字轉換為十進位數字符串。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"erfi66r0rmfpgag0iald7a67g\"><a href=\"api/common/PercentPipe\" title=\"PercentPipe | Common - API | Angular\"><code>PercentPipe</code></a></td>\n<td align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"awzxqtk8dec53jebxheiapj4l\">將數字轉換為百分比字串。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"use-datepipe-to-display-the-current-date\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6sw3sgoq7y3sdxm5ee5tdanom\">使用 DatePipe 顯示當前日期<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#use-datepipe-to-display-the-current-date\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2vczaphqyifgffypcmrsew6qq\">要以當前語言環境的格式顯示當前日期，請對 <code><a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">DatePipe</a></code> 使用以下格式。</p>\n<!--todo: replace with code-example -->\n<code-example format=\"typescript\" language=\"typescript\">\n\n{{ today | <a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">date</a> }}\n\n</code-example>\n<h2 id=\"override-current-locale-for-currencypipe\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4hjz8apugou1no334aipgvs80\">改寫 CurrencyPipe 的當前語言環境<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#override-current-locale-for-currencypipe\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7sprssqailub4fh7lqvcrylq6\">將 <code>locale</code> 引數新增到此通道以覆蓋 <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code> 令牌的當前值。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"760sy32tuyc9i2rpoygct9wkp\">要強制貨幣使用美式英語（<code>en-US</code>），請以如下格式使用 <code><a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">CurrencyPipe</a></code></p>\n<!--todo: replace with code-example -->\n<code-example format=\"typescript\" language=\"typescript\">\n\n{{ amount | <a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">currency</a> : 'en-US' }}\n\n</code-example>\n<div class=\"alert is-helpful\">\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"mz0isp0viyxutdngu1nu3xc6\"><strong>注意</strong>：<br>\n為 <code><a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">CurrencyPipe</a></code> 指定的語音環境設定會覆蓋應用程式的全域 <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code> 令牌。</p>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"whats-next\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"407r2fj2mi5kvg7imj9zdcpe\">下一步呢？<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#whats-next\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"epm9bh2huad0tqpeq9pgxefr3\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-prepare\" title=\"Prepare component for translation | Angular\">準備翻譯樣板</a></li>\n</ul>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最後複查時間：Mon Feb 28 2022</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/DatePipe\n - api/common/getLocaleExtraDayPeriodRules\n - api/common/getLocaleExtraDayPeriods\n - api/common/registerLocaleData\n - guide/i18n-common-locale-id\n - guide/i18n-common-overview\n - guide/pipes\n - guide/pipes-overview\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe\n - api/common/DatePipe\n - api/common/DecimalPipe\n - api/common/PercentPipe\n - api/core/LOCALE_ID\n - guide/glossary#pipe\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#format-data-based-on-locale\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#override-current-locale-for-currencypipe\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#use-datepipe-to-display-the-current-date\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#whats-next\n - guide/i18n-common-prepare\n-->"}